# prisma.config.ts file is loaded directly by the Prisma CLI (via its own ts runner) and
# is intentionally excluded from the package's tsconfig.json (which only covers
# src/ for compilation). Including it would violate the `rootDir: "src"` constraint.
# See: https://www.prisma.io/docs/guides/turborepo#22-initialize-prisma-and-define-models
**/prisma.config.ts